subject: Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: BMW-Sauber protested the legality of cars used by the Brawn, Toyota and Williams teams at the Malaysian Grand Prix in a repeat of actions taken by others in Australia last week. Race stewards again rejected the protest, just as officials had in Melbourne. BMW-Sauber said it would appeal.
